E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Lost MC, man. Round up the wrecking crew.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~失落帮万岁，哥们。叫上弟兄们一起。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I hope I don't get sick cos' of that shit.
~z~I'm drunken man - I should get home. Let's go.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~我喝多了，哥们。我该回家了。咱们走吧。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I gotta sleep this shit off man,
~z~Let's show 'em how we do it in the Lost MC. Go get some brothers.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~让他们看看咱们失落帮的规矩。叫几个弟兄来。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~It's not what we said, but okay.
~z~Looks like we picked up some bitches.
~z~We should have finished at the table man.
~z~You hungry man? Okay, I could eat.
~z~Jonathan, you're late. Let's ride out, man.
~z~I guess this dump will have to do us.
~z~Sure, I can handle a quick drink.

E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~没想到你是个半途而废的人。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Nothing mixes better than cards and booze. Apart from guns and booze...
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~喝酒打牌是绝配，仅次于打枪配喝酒...

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Okay Johnny - you should have said if you wanted to come to the strip club.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~好嘛，Johnny，想来脱衣舞俱乐部你就直说嘛。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Air hockey? I'm drunk, what the fuck.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~桌上冰球？搞啥嘛，我都喝多了。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Alright, man. Let's hit 'em hard. Get some of the brothers.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~好了，哥们。玩就玩尽兴。再叫几个兄弟吧。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~You always was a lucky asshole, JK.
~z~I don't like that joint too much.
~z~Air hockey? Bit of a change, but fine.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~桌上冰球？没什么差别，也行吧。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Good to see you, brother, let's do this.
~z~This looks like an okay joint, man.
~z~I'd almost given you up for dead, brother.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~你再不来我都要当你死了了，兄弟。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Trust me, amigo - I was born with a dart in my hand.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~相信我，朋友，我生来就是玩飞镖的。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Man I'm so drunk any shit will seem good.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~哥们，酒喝多了，看啥都赏心悦目。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I nearly puked down that stripper's tits.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~我都要把那脱衣小妹的奶子吐出来了。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Air hockey and booze - what a match made in heaven.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~桌上冰球加啤酒，简直是天作之合啊。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I hope this show is good, man.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~希望这次的演出还不错，哥们。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Okay big boy, let's see what you got.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~好，大家伙，让我看看你有啥本事。
~z~不好意思，兄弟，都是爹妈生得好。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~That was fun, brother. Let's hang again soon
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~今天够嗨的，兄弟。过后再约啊。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I bet some brothers will want to join in on this ass kicking. Round 'em up.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~我打赌有兄弟也想来一起嗨。叫上他们。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Sorry, man, but someone has to lose.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~不好意思啊，哥们，不过总得有人输啊。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~A show could be fun... not what we said, but fun.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~演出应该有点意思...不是平常那个意思，就是有意思。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Man I love this kind of joint.
~z~We both know you're in the closet, amigo.
~z~That was good times, brother. See you soon
~z~This place has the best food, man.
~z~Man, nothing like a few drinks to make me think I can hustle at pool.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~哥们，酒足饭饱我必在台球桌上大杀四方。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I ain't down for this Johnny. Not now.
~z~Man, lucky no one died in there - I'm too drunk for darts.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~哥们，喝完酒了飞飞镖，还好没出人命。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Sure - I could watch a show, man.
~z~You think you can prove yourself this time, huh JK?
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~这回有没有把握证明自己够牛逼，JK？

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~That was kinda fun, I coulda stayed longer.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~有点意思啊，我还能多留一会儿。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~You need me to steal you a new watch, asshole?
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~要爷给你偷块新手表吗，混蛋？

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Okay, assholes. Good to fuckin' see ya.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~好啦，混蛋们，很高兴见到你们。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Don't mean to be an SOB, but you're late. Let's hit it.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~不是我说你，但迟到就是迟到。咱们走吧。
~z~临阵脱逃的人不可能赢，哥们。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Johnny I hate to break up a party, but I gotta get home.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~Johnny，我不想破坏大家聚会的气氛，但我真得回家了。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Man, I feel lucky about this game.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~哥们，我觉得这把是我运气好。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Let's see what you got in the way of air hockey skill, my friend.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~看看你的球技有几斤几两，我的朋友。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Brothers for life, Lost forever. Let's fuckin' do it.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~生死兄弟情，失落帮万岁。搞他妈的。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~That was pretty funny until you bailed.
~z~What is this bullshit man? It ain't what we said we was doing?
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~搞什么鬼哥们？咱不是说好了吗？

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Okay, Mr ADD - I was just warming up.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~好了，你个多动症，我只是在热身而已。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Shit - Jackie will kill me - Johnny - let's split.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~操，Jackie会杀了我的，Johnny，今天就散了吧。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Next time, let's finish the fucking game man.
~z~Hey we should have finished that shit.
~z~This ain't what we said man. What the fuck is wrong with you?
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~说好的可不是这样。你他妈怎么回事？

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I feel my luck is in tonight.
~z~Sure, I'll beat you at pool if you want.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~好啊，打台球找虐的话我奉陪。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~What we doing here, man? I ain't down with this shit.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~咱在这干啥呢，哥们？我来又不是为了这个。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Fuck yeah boys. Good to see your ugly faces.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~见到你们这帮臭逼真他妈好，伙计。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Man, I'm too drunk for more pool.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~哥们，喝了这么多还要打台球啊。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~We need numbers for this. Go get some of the boys.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~咱们多来点人吧。去叫几个伙计。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Man I'm too drunk for women - I should go back to my wife.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~哥们，我喝多了看不来妞，得回家陪老婆了。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~It's not chance, man. It's skill. I feel the cards.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~不是运气，哥们。这就是技术。我摸牌有灵性。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I can hardly see I'm so drunk - darts sounds perfect!
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~喝多了啥都看不清，最适合玩飞镖了！

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Every shot you played was a fluke man.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~你打的每一杆都是蒙的吧，哥们。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Not what you said, but I can hang.
~z~Johnny - it's been fun, but I've got a wife to be shouted at. Goodbye.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~Johnny，今天玩得很嗨，但老婆还在等着训我。再见。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Lucky asshole. You must live in a bar.
~z~Man I am still drunk as shit.
~z~I want to finish that shit man.
~z~I guess this establishment will have to suffice amigo.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~这次只能在这儿凑合了，兄弟们。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~This place is okay, if you don't mind stomach ache.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~不怕胃疼的话，这家店也还可以。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I'm either gonna sober up or puke up.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~我要不醒过来，要不就吐出来。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~You remember today. It won't happen again.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~今天这出你记住了，没有下次了。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Genius, come back when you've got a bike.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~睿智，没有摩托就别来碰头了。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Man - that place should be shut down.
~z~Man, I've got the drunken munchies bad.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~哥们，我酒喝多了正想垫垫肚子。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~I don't usually play pool with women.
~z~Man, I'm seeing triple. I-I gotta get outta here.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~哥们，我看东西都重影了，得走了。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Thanks man - that's a big change from being screamed at my old lady - let's hang soon.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~谢了哥们，出来玩和在家被老婆骂真是大不相同。晚点再约吧。

E1FCJ3A.original: ~z~Man, I'm still drunk as shit. I need to sleep.
E1FCJ3A.translated: ~z~哥们，我醉成一坨屎了，我得睡会。
~z~我放你一马你才打平局的，伙计。
